data.description:
Welcome to Beautiful Townhome in Lexington Square! This stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom house is located in the desirable area of Jacksonville, FL. Step inside and be greeted by a spacious and inviting living space, featuring new paint throughout. The bedrooms are conveniently situated on the second floor, providing privacy and tranquility. The open space kitchen boasts a breakfast bar, perfect for enjoying your morning coffee or entertaining guests. The dedicated dining area is ideal for hosting dinner parties or enjoying family meals. One of the highlights of this townhome is the enclosed screened patio, where you can relax and unwind after a long day. The fully fenced backyard offers privacy and space for outdoor activities. With off-street parking, you'll never have to worry about finding a spot for your vehicle. Another added convenience is the washer and dryer in unit, making laundry a breeze. 

Resident benefit package is required. Includes move-in concierge services, online portal access, document storage, multiple payment options, credit reporting and liability and personal property insurance. Monthly cost - $50.00 per month. Lease preparation fee - $125.00.
Pet friendly too! Approved pet okay with pet screening, monthly fee and $125 initial pet admin fee.

Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this beautiful townhome your new home. Contact us today to schedule a tour and experience the comfort and convenience of living in Lexington Square!
